Real-World Example: Sentiment Analysis
Input

"The product is amazing"

Step 1: Vectorization
[0.45, 0.82, 0.21]
Step 2: ML Algorithm

Logistic Regression analyzes the vector.

Step 3: Prediction
Positive Review 😊

