=============

Machine Learning algorithms are mathematical models that learn patterns from numerical data (vectors) and make predictions. 
In NLP, algorithms such as Naive Bayes, Logistic Regression, SVM, and Neural Networks are used for tasks like spam detection, 
sentiment analysis, text classification, and chatbots

=============

Text → Vector → ML Algorithm → Prediction

Example:

"I love this product"
→ TF-IDF Vector
→ Logistic Regression
→ Positive Review 😊

